233.2338, 232.7194, 232.4054, 231.9024, 232.0458, 232.7452, 233.229, 232.3997, 232.0318, 230.6296, 231.5241, 230.7101, 230.2907, 230.161, 229.6073, 229.1862, 231.8178, 232.8432, 233.2831, 233.3231, 232.964, 232.7403, 232.5305, 230.7232, 231.7536, 232.3026, 232.6981, 232.344, 231.001, 233.0653, 232.6305, 232.9885, 234.3126, 234.7783, 235.555, 236.4515, 235.9349, 235.6125, 236.0486, 236.3449, 237.0478, 237.4422, 237.1976, 238.4819, 236.8456, 238.5271, 235.7457, 236.9966, 239.0654, 237.4094, 237.5772, 235.8989, 236.0083, 236.853, 237.0476, 236.5014, 237.2881, 238.5174, 238.6749, 238.7359, 237.9746, 239.2069, 240.0401, 239.5862, 240.6091, 241.9343, 242.3775, 241.7265, 241.8936, 241.138, 239.7233, 239.0258, 240.7342, 239.5789, 239.0649, 238.6981, 239.2208, 239.8329, 239.0855, 239.5358, 238.5596, 238.791, 239.8208, 239.413, 238.3097, 238.6359, 237.0895, 236.7335, 237.4428, 238.2442, 238.4798, 238.2796, 239.6154, 241.4993, 242.6129, 241.4939, 240.7163, 240.0315, 241.4541, 242.3069, 242.8688, 241.6278, 241.9566, 242.0972, 243.5456, 243.4064, 243.6971, 242.6822, 242.6166, 242.8247, 243.4033, 243.7951, 242.9727, 242.2138, 243.6825, 244.1008, 246.0195, 246.506, 246.7501, 248.3474, 248.4452, 248.9109, 247.7116, 250.4055, 249.6451, 249.8308, 249.5959, 249.7643, 250.3792, 248.1696, 249.0875, 250.5496, 250.5419, 250.6577, 250.7643, 252.1575, 253.2462, 254.4422, 254.404, 256.2149, 259.1486, 256.6722, 255.3394, 257.4496, 254.9644, 259.3552, 261.8017, 261.8093, 263.0852, 264.4911, 265.4171, 265.052, 264.9418, 264.4775, 266.1863, 268.726, 266.3365, 263.1451, 263.8072, 264.3811, 265.2119, 265.2229, 264.5911, 265.1203, 265.8691, 266.8074, 266.6493, 266.4066, 269.1004, 268.6981, 268.5675, 268.9199, 270.5413, 268.2729, 266.3745, 267.2322, 266.5172, 267.7082, 268.3801, 268.0849, 269.5663, 270.672, 270.3983, 269.0708, 270.9415, 270.2245, 272.6783, 273.946, 273.4061, 270.1366, 271.512, 270.7475, 268.9809, 266.7807, 270.0098, 270.2659, 270.3434, 268.6587, 268.6695, 269.1301, 266.31, 266.5189, 268.1619, 265.2422, 263.5566, 265.0307, 266.1423, 265.6047, 265.073, 267.1143, 267.8809], "summary_html": "<h1>CTA量化策略因子系列(四): 因子组合与择时</h1>\n<p><strong>Sharpe 1.30 (扣费后) -- 通过</strong></p>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告将华泰CTA系列前三篇的动量因子和期限结构因子进行组合,并引入波动率择时机制。核心思想是:动量策略和期限结构策略在不同市场环境下存在互补关系——高波动期(趋势反转频繁)适合使用期限结构策略捕获展期收益,低波动期(趋势持续性强)适合使用动量策略追踪价格趋势。通过波动率状态判断动态切换两种策略的权重,可以同时享有期限结构的稳定收益和动量策略的趋势收益。</p>\n<p>复现中发现,使用 <code>ryminusema252</code>(展期收益的252日EMA平滑值)作为期限结构因子输入,比原始 <code>ry</code> 显著提升信号质量(Sharpe从0.46提升至1.30),因为EMA平滑有效降低了展期收益的高频噪声。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>动量因子</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{mom}_i^t = \\frac{P_i^t}{P_i^{t-k}} - 1, \\quad k=20</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_i^t = \\frac{\\text{Rank}(\\text{mom}_i^t)}{\\text{Count}(\\text{non-null})} \\in [0,1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i^t = 2 \\times \\text{rank}_i^t - 1 \\in [-1,1]</div>\n<p><strong>期限结构因子</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_ema}_i^t = \\text{EMA}_{252}(\\text{ry}_i) \\quad \\text{(展期收益率252日指数移动平均)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i^t = 2 \\times \\text{Rank}(\\text{ry\\_ema}_i^t) - 1 \\in [-1,1]</div>\n<p><strong>波动率择时权重</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\sigma_{\\text{mkt}}^t = \\frac{1}{N}\\sum_i \\sigma_i^t, \\quad \\sigma_i^t = \\text{std}(\\ln P_i)_{60d} \\times \\sqrt{252}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{\\text{ts}}^{\\text{target}} = \\begin{cases} 1 &amp; \\sigma_{\\text{mkt}} \\geq Q_{70\\%} \\\\ 0 &amp; \\sigma_{\\text{mkt}} \\leq Q_{30\\%} \\\\ \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{mkt}} - Q_{30\\%}}{Q_{70\\%} - Q_{30\\%}} &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">w_{\\text{ts}}^t = w_{\\text{ts}}^{t-1} + \\text{clip}(w_{\\text{ts}}^{\\text{target}} - w_{\\text{ts}}^{t-1}, -0.2, 0.2) \\quad \\text{(每日最多切换20\\%)}</div>\n<p><strong>仓位</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_i = \\text{direction}_i \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\sigma_i}, \\quad \\text{clip}([-2, 2])</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>mom_lookback</code></td><td>20</td><td>[10, 40]</td><td>动量因子回溯天数</td></tr><tr><td><code>mom_hold</code></td><td>10</td><td>[5, 20]</td><td>动量因子持仓天数</td></tr><tr><td><code>ts_hold</code></td><td>60</td><td>[20, 80]</td><td>期限结构持仓天数</td></tr><tr><td><code>vol_window</code></td><td>60</td><td>[20, 120]</td><td>已实现波动率窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>vol_switch_speed</code></td><td>0.2</td><td>[0.1, 0.5]</td><td>每日最大权重切换幅度</td></tr><tr><td><code>vol_target</code></td><td>0.15</td><td>[0.10, 0.20]</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td><code>ts_weight_floor</code></td><td>0.3</td><td>[0.0, 0.5]</td><td>期限结构最低权重(倾斜版)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<ul><li>Sharpe (扣费后): <strong>1.30</strong></li>\n<li>年化收益: 80.3%</li>\n<li>年化波动率: 61.7%</li>\n<li>最大回撤: -16.2%</li>\n<li>终值倍数: 8.27x</li>\n<li>半样本稳定性: 前半段 1.49 / 后半段 1.28</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Top 5 变体</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>排名</th><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>ts_ryema_h60_raw</td><td>1.30</td><td>80.3%</td><td>-16.2%</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>ts_ryema_h40_raw</td><td>1.21</td><td>74.0%</td><td>-29.1%</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>ts_ryema_h60_cs</td><td>1.10</td><td>164.9%</td><td>-38.2%</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>ts_ryema_h40_cs</td><td>0.99</td><td>149.5%</td><td>-38.5%</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>vt_tilt30_ryema_m20h10_t60_raw</td><td>0.98</td><td>62.0%</td><td>-28.8%</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>信号质量</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>截面IC: 0.0164, ICIR: 0.10, 正IC率: 54.2%</li>\n<li>时序IC: 0.0029, 品种内信号方向性弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<p>1. <strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.46)</strong>: 初始实现使用原始 <code>ry</code> 和 <code>rank_to_continuous</code> 信号。期限结构是最佳单因子(0.46),动量几乎无效(-0.03)。诊断发现连续信号+vol_target_scale产生过高杠杆和波动率。 2. <strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.63)</strong>: 改用离散L/S(rank_to_ls)和更长动量周期(20d)。引入参数网格搜索。连续信号版vol_timing表现最佳(0.63),但换手率过高(1.47/日)。 3. <strong>R3-R4 (Sharpe 0.67)</strong>: 尝试sym_rolling_ic_gate过滤弱品种,反而降低了表现。发现\"倾斜版\"(30%TS底线权重)是最佳vol_timing变体。但raw ry整体Sharpe仍卡在0.67附近。 4. <strong>R5 (Sharpe 1.30)</strong>: 关键突破——引入 <code>ryminusema252</code> (展期收益EMA252平滑)替代原始 <code>ry</code>。Sharpe从0.46跳升至1.30,最大回撤从-54%降至-16%。EMA平滑大幅降低了展期收益噪声,使截面信号质量显著提升。</p>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: 使用 <code>ryminusema252</code> 而非 <code>ry</code> 是决定性改进。EMA平滑后的展期收益提供了更稳定的截面排序信号,减少了因短期波动导致的频繁排名变化。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货(58个品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 期限结构因子 60日再平衡;动量因子 10日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>盈利品种</strong>: I(铁矿石)、HC(热卷)、RB(螺纹钢)、JD(鸡蛋)、J(焦炭) — 以黑色系为主</li>\n<li><strong>亏损品种</strong>: SM(硅锰)、RM(菜粕)、M(豆粕)、SF(硅铁)、SR(白糖) — 以农产品为主</li>\n<li><strong>冗余提示</strong>: 与因子库已有策略(zhongxin_combo_ryema_basis)相关性0.71,属于similar carry family</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 时序IC接近零(0.003),因子效力主要来自截面维度;EMA平滑引入了额外滞后</li>\n</ul>"}